lyrics:
[verse]
Lucas Pukas Mucas, a wild soul unknown
Lost in the chaos, a world on his own
Searching for meaning amidst the vast sea
In Lucas' journey lies a mystery

[chorus]
Lucas, oh Lucas, yearning to be free
Break the chains that bind, and let your spirit flee
Embrace the unknown, let your dreams set sail
Lucas Pukas Mucas, rise above, prevail
